1
00:00:01.873 --> 00:00:02.699
In this module,

2
00:00:02.699 --> 00:00:05.962
I covered an example of deploying a JHipster application to production.

3
00:00:05.962 --> 00:00:06.315
First,

4
00:00:06.315 --> 00:00:10.434
I showed you the list of Spring profile constants that are

5
00:00:10.434 --> 00:00:13.231
provided out of the box by JHipster.

6
00:00:13.231 --> 00:00:15.861
This included environment-based profiles for dev,

7
00:00:15.861 --> 00:00:21.463
test, and prod, as well as feature-based profiles for swagger and Liquibase.

8
00:00:21.463 --> 00:00:25.806
Next, I covered making changes in the generated project configuration files.

9
00:00:25.806 --> 00:00:29.211
Changes were made both to a production properties file,

10
