and the logging configuration file.

11
00:00:30.773 --> 00:00:31.086
Then,

12
00:00:31.086 --> 00:00:35.340
I showed you how to run Microsoft SQL Server using a docker

13
00:00:35.340 --> 00:00:37.834
configuration generated for you by JHipster.

14
00:00:37.834 --> 00:00:42.307
Finally, I demonstrated running the JHipster project as an executable WAR file.

15
00:00:42.307 --> 00:00:47.374
I showed you how to build the WAR, and execute it directly from a command line.

16
00:00:47.374 --> 00:00:48.445
